    "auto_key_212": "Shri Panchayati Akhara Shri Niranjani is not just an ascetic tradition but a living spiritual heritage of Sanatan Dharma. Its spiritual practice, scriptures, Guru tradition and the spirit of protection of religion inspire millions of devotees even today.",
    "auto_key_213": "classical tradition",
