    "auto_key_227": "Shri Panchayati Akhara is the main Akhara of Shri Niranjani Dashnami Shaiv ​​Sannyasa tradition. It was established with the aim of protecting religion, culture, Vedas, Sanyas tradition and nationalism. Even today this Akhara is playing a leading role in spiritual practice, Guru-disciple tradition and preservation of Sanatan culture.",
