    "auto_key_236": "Shri Panchayati Akhara Shri Niranjani – Immortal symbol of Sanatan Sadhana",
    "auto_key_237": "Shri Panchayati Akhara Shri Niranjani is not just an Akhara, but a living center of Sanatan Dharma, Veda-Vedanta, penance, renunciation and Guru-disciple tradition. It was established with the objective of protecting religion, organization of saint society and spreading spiritual consciousness. Even today the Akhara is continuously dedicated to the service of the nation, culture and humanity.",
